== 漫畫的引用 ==
電影導演、監製兼漫畫作家的[[凱文·史密斯|凱文·史密斯]]認為《驚心動魄》很像一本名為《{{le|Mage (漫畫)|Mage (comics)|Mage: The Hero Discovered}}》，內容敘述某神秘人試圖說服一名-{普通人}-，藉此查證他是個超級英雄。《驚心動魄》和《Mage》的故事都設定在費城，《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》的{{le|艾維斯·米契|Elvis Mitchell}}提到，片中披著雨衣的大衛·杜恩在巡邏的視覺畫面與[[DC漫畫|DC漫畫]]的角色[[幽靈_(DC漫畫)|幽靈]]相似<ref name=comic>{{cite news | author = Scott Brown | title = Comic Belief | url = http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,90839,00.html | work = [[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] | date = 2000-12-06 | accessdate = 2008-12-19 | archive-date = 2009-04-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090427201626/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,90839,00.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

作為漫畫的主角有其配色和別名。大衛的是綠色，並可稱為「安全」（雨衣的字樣）或「英雄」（報紙給他的稱呼），伊利亞則是紫色和「玻璃-{}-先生」。這些顏色在他們的衣服、房子壁紙、床單及個人物品上可見。幾個場景能見到，透過反射或縫隙來讓人物表演，類似漫畫分鏡。

== 迴響 ==
=== 評價 ===
《驚心動魄》整體獲得的評價多為正面。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據166篇評論，新鮮度69%，平均得分6.3／10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/unbreakable/ |title=Unbreakable (2000) |publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |date= |accessdate=2017-01-03 |archive-date=2010-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100806165947/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/unbreakable/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分62，評價以正面居多<ref>[http://www.metacritic.com/movie/unbreakable Unbreakable (2000)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/unbreakable |date=20161213112052 }} Metacritic（2017-01-03）.</ref>。《驚心動魄》常被稱讚其陰謀式的給予觀眾不可預知的懸念，讓人覺得有點像是《[[靈異第六感|靈異第六感]]》。

儘管多數人都給予電影好評，但在影評人間卻有些兩極；[[羅傑·伊伯特|羅傑·伊伯特]]表示自己喜歡這部電影，但對結局感到失望。伊伯特認為，威利「微妙的演技」與他平時演出的「無腦動作片」大為不同<ref>{{cite news | author = Roger Ebert | title = Unbreakable | url = http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20001122/REVIEWS/11220302/1023 | work = [[Chicago_Sun-Times|Chicago Sun-Times]] | date = 2000-11-22 | accessdate = 2008-12-20 | authorlink = Roger Ebert | archive-date = 2013-03-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130311055124/http://rogerebert.suntimes.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20001122%2FREVIEWS%2F11220302%2F1023 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》的{{le|肯尼斯·圖蘭|Kenneth Turan}}認為該片太像《靈異第六感》<ref>{{cite news | author = Kenneth Turan | url = http://www.calendarlive.com/movies/reviews/cl-movie001121-3,0,4110177.story | work = [[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] | title = An 'Unbreakable' Sense of Déjà Vu | date = 2000-11-21 | accessdate = 2008-12-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080622010752/http://www.calendarlive.com/movies/reviews/cl-movie001121-3%2C0%2C4110177.story | archivedate = 2008-06-22 | authorlink = Kenneth Turan | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，對比之下《驚心動魄》並不出色。而《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》的陶德·麥卡錫則批評了沙馬蘭的劇本和演員們的演出，但稱讚{{le|狄倫·提切諾|Dylan Tichenor}}的剪輯和[[詹姆斯·紐頓·霍華|詹姆斯·紐頓·霍華]]所創作的配樂<ref>{{cite news | author = Todd McCarthy | url = http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117788668.html | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | title = Unbreakable | date = 2000-11-20 | accessdate = 2008-12-20}}</ref>。

沙馬蘭承認，他對於《驚心動魄》從影評人那獲得的評價感到失望<ref name=sequel>{{cite news | author = Daniel Fierman | title = Night of the Living Dread | url = http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,333419,00.html | work = [[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] | date = 2002-08-02 | accessdate = 2008-12-19 | archive-date = 2007-05-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070516184431/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,333419,00.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。沙馬蘭也對[[試金石影業|試金石影業]]的營銷感到不滿，因為他想主打《驚心動魄》像是部漫畫改編的超級英雄電影，但試金石影業卻堅持宣傳是一部[[心理驚悚片|心理驚悚片]]，就如同《靈異第六感》一樣<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.nytimes.com/2008/06/02/business/media/02night.html |title= Shyamalan's Hollywood Horror Story — NYTimes.com |publisher= www.nytimes.com |accessdate= 2009-01-23 |last= Weiner |first= Allison Hope |date= 2008-06-02 |archive-date= 2014-12-30 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141230143849/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/06/02/business/media/02night.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

2009年，奧斯卡獲獎導演[[昆汀·塔倫提諾|昆汀·塔倫提諾]]給予了《驚心動魄》讚賞，並列入1992年以來（他成為導演後）公佈的前20名電影名單上。塔倫提諾認為，這可能是布魯斯·威利最佳的演出，並認為該片的宣傳方向是錯的；他表示，如果電影的宣傳標語為「如果超人在地球上，根本不會知道他是超人？」會更好<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.spike.com/video/tarantinos-top-20/3228451|title=Tarantino's Top 20 Movies Since 1992|accessdate=2009-08-17|work=[[Spike_(TV_channel)|Spike (TV channel)]]|publisher=|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090820231204/http://www.spike.com/video/tarantinos-top-20/3228451|archivedate=2009-08-20}}</ref>。2011年，《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》將其列入在任何時刻的十大超級英雄電影中的第四名，稱它是最好的超級英雄起源故事之一，並有著「相當安靜、含蓄和現實的外觀，來做為一名超級英雄」<ref name="time_top10"/>。

=== 票房 ===
《驚心動魄》在美國於2000年11月22日上映，其首映週末從兩千七百零八間戲院中獲得3030萬美元的票房，位居當週亞軍。電影下檔後，美國總票房收入為9500萬美元，而海外為1.53億美元，全球總計2.481億美元；對比7500萬美元的成本來說還算成功<ref name="boxofficemojo_unbreakable"/>。

== 續集 ==
電影上映後，在粉絲網站和媒體間開始謠傳將電影會推出續集。2000年，布魯斯·威利表示，希望《驚心動魄》能推出三部曲<ref name="Shya">{{cite news | author = Brian Linder | url = http://movies.ign.com/articles/036/036655p1.html | title = Willis' Unbreakable Trilogy Hopes Shattered | work = [[IGN|IGN]] | date = 2000-12-05 | accessdate = 2008-12-20 | archive-date = 2008-10-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081011173641/http://movies.ign.com/articles/036/036655p1.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2000年12月，沙馬蘭否認了他將編寫《驚心動魄》三部曲的傳聞，他說，他甚至沒有考慮這件事<ref name="Shya" />。2001年8月，沙馬蘭透露，由於DVD銷售上的成功，他曾找過試金石影業談過推出續集的想法，但試金石似乎認為電影的票房不會成功<ref>{{cite news | author = Olly Richards | url = http://www.empireonline.com/News/story.asp?nid=13123 | title = An Unbreakable Sequel? | work = [[Empire_(magazine)|Empire Online]] | date = 2001-08-01 | accessdate = 2008-12-20 | archive-date = 2012-03-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120323151651/http://www.empireonline.com/News/story.asp?nid=13123 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2008年9月，沙馬蘭與山繆·傑克森表示，目前，我們正在對電影的續集作出一些討論，但因票房表現不夠令人滿意而受阻。傑克森說，他有意拍續集，但沙馬蘭則不置可否<ref name="seijas">{{cite news | author = Casey Seijas | url = http://splashpage.mtv.com/2008/09/18/samuel-l-jackson-m-night-shyamalan-on-the-unbreakable-sequel-that-never-was-but-might-be/ | title = Samuel L. Jackson, M. Night Shyamalan On The ‘Unbreakable’ Sequel That Never Was, But Might Be | work = [[MTV_News|MTV News]] | date = 2008-09-18 | accessdate = 2008-12-20 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090115075126/http://splashpage.mtv.com/2008/09/18/samuel-l-jackson-m-night-shyamalan-on-the-unbreakable-sequel-that-never-was-but-might-be/ | archivedate = 2009-01-15 }}</ref>。2010年2月，威利表示，他仍與[[山繆·傑克森|山繆·傑克森]]進行討論，如果傑克森也能夠參加最好<ref>{{cite web |title=Bruce Willis Says M. Night Shyamalan 'Still Thinking' About 'Unbreakable 2' |first=Rick |last=Marshall |work=[[MTV_News|MTV News]] |publisher=[[Viacom|Viacom]] |date=2010-02-22 |url=http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/02/22/bruce-willis-says-m-night-shyamalan-still-thinking-about-unbreakable-2/ |accessdate=2010-06-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100425235248/http://splashpage.mtv.com/2010/02/22/bruce-willis-says-m-night-shyamalan-still-thinking-about-unbreakable-2/ |archivedate=2010-04-25 }}<br />{{cite web |title='Unbreakable 2' on the Horizon? |first=Bill |last=Gibron |work=[[PopMatters|PopMatters]] |date=2010-02-24 |url=http://www.popmatters.com/pm/post/121312-unbreakable-2-on-the-horizon/ |accessdate=2010-06-12 |archive-date=2010-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100327225710/http://www.popmatters.com/pm/post/121312-unbreakable-2-on-the-horizon |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 2010年9月，沙馬蘭透露，第一部電影的第二計劃的反派已被移到了續集的計畫中，但該角色已被用在他即將開始製作的電影中。

而到了沙馬蘭的2017年恐怖驚悚片《[[分裂_(2016年電影)|分裂]]》乃確認為《驚心動魄》的主題續集，片尾也表明兩部電影完全屬於同一世界觀<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://screencrush.com/split-review-m-night-shyamalans-best-film-in-years-is-a-surprisingly-poignant-thriller/ |title=‘Split’ Review: M. Night Shyamalan’s Best Film in Years Is a Surprisingly Poignant Thriller |author=Britt Hayes |date=2016-09-26 |access-date=2016-10-27 |archive-date=2016-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161027193830/http://screencrush.com/split-review-m-night-shyamalans-best-film-in-years-is-a-surprisingly-poignant-thriller/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，該片於2017年1月20日在美國廣泛上映<ref name=ReleaseDate>{{cite news|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=M. Night Shyamalan’s Next Movie Titled ‘Split,’ Set for January, 2017 Release|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/m-night-shyamalan-split-january-1201627822/|accessdate=2015-12-08|work=variety.com|date=2015-10-27|archive-date=2015-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210222938/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/m-night-shyamalan-split-january-1201627822/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年1月，沙馬蘭在受訪時仍表示自己希望可推出《驚心動魄》的直接續集，並已經有了故事大綱<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ew.com/movies/2017/01/20/split-m-night-shyamalan-ending-interview/?xid=entertainment-weekly_socialflow_twitter |title=Split spoiler: M. Night Shyamalan breaks down film's shock ending |author=Joe McGovern |date=2017-01-20 |access-date=2017-01-20 |archive-date=2017-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170126141513/http://ew.com/movies/2017/01/20/split-m-night-shyamalan-ending-interview/?xid=entertainment-weekly_socialflow_twitter |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2017年4月26日，沙馬蘭在自己的[[Twitter|Twitter]]頁面上透露，第三部電影命名為《[[異裂_(電影)|異裂]]》，電影於2019年1月18日在美國上映，而演員[[布魯斯·威利|布魯斯·威利]]、[[山繆·傑克森|山繆·傑克森]]、[[詹姆斯·麥艾維|詹姆斯·麥艾維]]和[[安雅·泰勒-喬伊|安雅·泰勒-喬伊]]都回歸出演自己的角色<ref name="cb glass">{{cite web|url=http://www.cinemablend.com/news/1651749/the-unbreakable-and-split-crossover-movie-reveals-official-title-and-four-stars|title=The Unbreakable And Split Crossover Movie Reveals Official Title And Four Stars|date=2017-04-26|publisher=|accessdate=2017-04-27|archive-date=2017-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170427100819/http://www.cinemablend.com/news/1651749/the-unbreakable-and-split-crossover-movie-reveals-official-title-and-four-stars|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="thr sept2017">{{Cite web | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/m-night-shyamalans-glass-adds-unbreakable-actors-1041929 | title = M. Night Shyamalan's 'Glass' Adds 'Unbreakable' Actors | first = Broys | last = Kit | date = 2017-09-21 | accessdate = 2017-09-21 | work = [[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | archive-date = 2017-09-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170921222158/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/m-night-shyamalans-glass-adds-unbreakable-actors-1041929 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

